 <purpose>The Contract application module supports the requirement to record the identification of the contract or agreement under which product data is created or modified.</purpose>

 <inscope>
<li>creating and identifying the contract;</li>
<li>associating product data to the contract;</li>
<li>identifying the contract the optional organization or person in organization that assigned the identification to the contract;</li>
<li>identifying the contract the optional date or date and time when the contract was signed;</li>
<li>identifying the contract the optional approvals for a contract.</li>
 </inscope>

 <outscope>
 <li>all things which are not involved in the representation of contract information and applying it to product data.</li>
 </outscope>

